Coupling Analysis and Recommendations
AI can analyze different types of coupling and provide specific recommendations for reducing it.
Types of Coupling AI Can Identify:

Data Coupling: Classes that share complex data structures
Stamp Coupling: Classes that pass unnecessary data
Control Coupling: Classes that control each other's behavior
Content Coupling: Classes that access each other's internal data
Common Coupling: Classes that share global data

